msgid "Cleaner Key Management"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topics/releases/0.9.0.rst:75
msgid ""
"This release changes some of the key naming to allow for multiple master "
"keys to be held based on the type of minion gathering the master key."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topics/releases/0.9.0.rst:78
msgid ""
"The -d option has also been added to the salt-key command allowing for easy "
"removal of accepted public keys."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topics/releases/0.9.0.rst:81
msgid ""
"The --gen-keys option is now available as well for salt-key, this allows for"
" a salt specific RSA key pair to be easily generated from the command line."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topics/releases/0.9.0.rst:85
msgid "Improved 0MQ Master Workers"
